whereas.text:
Whereas around the United States, there have been many incidents of violent acts, some leading to
			 serious injury and death, committed by people under the influence of
			 synthetic drugs;

Whereas a lack of public understanding of the potential harm of synthetic drugs makes raising
			 public awareness about the dangers posed by such drugs extremely
			 important;

Whereas deceptive marketing by sellers of synthetic drugs and easy access to synthetic drugs online
			 and in many convenience stores create a false perception, particularly
			 among youth, that synthetic drugs are legal and safer than street drugs;

Whereas according to the 2012 Monitoring the Future survey of youth drug-use trends, 1 in every 9
			 United States high school seniors surveyed admitted to using synthetic
			 marijuana in the past year;
